      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s just so relentless. every morning i wake up and remember he’s not here and it’s like being hit by something heavy all over again. there’s no \"relief\" from just talking. i just want the void to stop being so loud. i honestly feel like i’m just existing for nothing. is it even wrong to just want to let go of everything?",
